{"tid":451893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"潔癖賊怕弄髒衣服　先脫光後爆竊","createTime":"2017-10-29T16:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-29T16:20:32.000Z","uid":150685,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"162da71a9256b78aa5956008809e72e06517c90d","tid":451893,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:06:10.000Z","msg":"廣東東莞一名楊姓男子日前趁夜色，到一間店舖行竊。令人感到匪夷所思的是，愛乾淨的他由於擔心衣服被弄髒，竟脫掉衣服，「光脫脫」地從鐵閘縫隙鑽進店內，行竊出來後才將衣服穿上。警方接報後經查，發現楊男從今年8月起作案9宗，共盜取3.64萬元人民幣和一手機。目前，楊男已經落網。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171029/photo/bkncn-20171029071035434-1029_05011_001_01p.jpg?20171029071320\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171029%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20171029071035434-1029_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20171029071320&h=4a74c4b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171029/photo/bkncn-20171029071035434-1029_05011_001_02b.jpg?20171029071320\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171029%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20171029071035434-1029_05011_001_02b.jpg%3F20171029071320&h=fe8e383d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171029/photo/bkncn-20171029071035434-1029_05011_001_03b.jpg?20171029071320\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171029%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20171029071035434-1029_05011_001_03b.jpg%3F20171029071320&h=7fab5d1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"abbfbc1f7511435c7b5b485989570d5897e4b9cc","tid":451893,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2de9068f86811b2840bef1405cc5c9445d2d404","tid":451893,"uid":51509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:07:51.000Z","msg":"本身污糟嘅人唔著衫就會乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 